      <title>美联储锁定 9 月降息 25 个基点：学院的 Tchir</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/fed-locked-in-on-25-bps-september-cut-academy-s-tchir-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Academy Securities 宏观策略主管 Peter Tchir 表示，美联储需要看到就业报告大幅走弱，才能在 9 月份降息 50 个基点，并关注降息对风险资产的影响。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/fed-locked-in-on-25-bps-september-cut-academy-s-tchir-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 11:00:25 GMT</pubDate>
