    <item>
      <title>Aker BP 称挪威石油产量与可再生能源发展齐头并进</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/norway-oil-output-renewable-push-go-hand-in-hand-aker-bp-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威第二大石油和天然气公司的负责人表示，挪威必须提供更多的区域用于碳氢化合物勘探，并扩大该国新兴的可再生能源行业，以保护国内零部件和服务供应商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/norway-oil-output-renewable-push-go-hand-in-hand-aker-bp-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:24:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚反对派政府因银行纠纷停止所有石油生产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/libyan-rival-government-to-stop-oil-output-amid-central-bank-row</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利比亚东部政府表示，在位于的黎波里的对手更换央行领导层后，将关闭所有石油生产和出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/libyan-rival-government-to-stop-oil-output-amid-central-bank-row</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威财富基金向 CIP 可再生能源基金注资 9 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/norway-s-wealth-fund-marks-900-million-for-cip-renewables-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威 1.7 万亿美元的主权财富基金承诺向哥本哈根基础设施合作伙伴的第五个旗舰基金投资 9 亿欧元（10 亿美元），这是该基金首次间接入股其非上市的可再生能源基础设施投资组合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/norway-s-wealth-fund-marks-900-million-for-cip-renewables-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:15:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
